item.dc:creator: @ringer24 ringer24
item.description:
@ringer24 wrote:

Considering i got “warned” I guess I’ll explain my reasoning.

  1. He asked a really dumb question in my opinion. I mean an account called a “skiller” could mean anything! I mean isn’t one of the main points in runescape to raise your skills? I mean yes people refer to skillers as low levels with high skill, but common I have a point.

  2. “A good account” - Thats exactly what i mean. A good rs account has some decent skills like Woodcut mining. Plus some good combat stats.
